transcription.text:
Speaker 1: I am trying to cancel a subscription that I have with you guys and I don't see an option.

Speaker 2: To do that online.

Speaker 1: What's your last name and your zip code so I can pull up your account?

Speaker 2: Cameron, C-A-M-E-R-O-N, 98178.

Speaker 1: Okay, I pulled up your profile, so I do want to mention you're currently one of our VIP members for the AG Viagra.

Speaker 2: The moment it does get canceled out, you wouldn't be able to order in the future, so what I could always offer you if you want, we can always put you under a six-month freeze plan.

Speaker 1: That way you can freeze it out and then when you do require it on the road, you can always access them.

Speaker 2: No, I want to cancel it.

Speaker 1: It doesn't work for me.

Speaker 2: No worries.

Speaker 1: I'll go ahead and put a stop to those orders and just keep in mind the prescription would be deleted and you wouldn't be allowed to order in the future.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: Have a good one.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
